
So i like to draw in class. I mean, who doesn't? And i draw some pretty graphic stuff. Not the "bad" stuff, but gore and shit. So i was drawing in math class and my teacher comes over and hands me mah homework, which was fine, but then this went down.
Teacher: okay, Nat, here is the homework from tuesday, oh, i see you have your notebook? Whoops, not a notebook, but those are good drawings.
Me: ...
He. Looked. In. My. Sketchbook.